LicenseActivationNumber

Activation number, given by the server if the license has been activated

LicenseDeviceName

Not supposed to be stored, a unique (or not) name for this device, to associate with this license activation and check sometimes to verify the license has not been copied on an other computer (you can use the device name, the ID of the computer or its hard drive, ...)

LicenseEmail

User email, given by the user with its license number when registering the software

LicenseNumber

License number, given by the user with its email address when registering the software
